actionGrowOlder_Utick() - Method in class thing.C_Vegetation
Compute the change of biomass given the level of rain in the cell.
The model follow a logistic law : biomass <- biomass(t-1) * (1 + growth_rate * ( 1 - biomass(t-1) / carrying_capacity)) Version J.Le Fur & M.Sall, 02-03 2016
